Using s3 load the dump into finance-db-03-alma8-olly-drx-kc.ssnc-corp.cloud
Load the content into financial DB. 

Then, test from finance-db-03-alma8-olly-drx-kc.ssnc-corp.cloud to finance-db-04-alma9-olly-drx-kc.ssnc-corp.cloud

on 17 server, 
/usr/pgsql-17/bin/pg_basebackup -Xs -c fast -R -v -D /apps/lib/pgsql/17/data -h 10.222.103.222

